<div class="about-main-page">
  <div class="head">
    <h1>
      <% title 'About Us' %>Welcome to Aviary!</h1>
    <p><%= description 'Aviary is a new hosted platform that allows users to easily discover and navigate audiovisual content.
      Whether you are a researcher trying to find specific audiovisual resources for your work, an organization trying
      to enhance discoverability of your collections, or a user who wants to watch content online, Aviary offers
      advanced tools to display, describe, and search audio and video.' %></p>
  </div>
  <div class="image">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>The Aviary Ecosystem</h2>
      <%= image_tag("https://#{ENV['S3_HOST_CDN']}/public/about-image.png") %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="annotations">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="image-holder">
            <%= image_tag("https://#{ENV['S3_HOST_CDN']}/public/annotations-image.png") %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="text">
            <h3>Annotations</h3>
            <p>Available in our next release, user-based, fully searchable annotations <br> will be available
              for all Aviary elements.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="users">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>The Aviary Users</h2>
      <article>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="img-holder">
              <%= image_tag("https://#{ENV['S3_HOST_CDN']}/public/pub-user.png") %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="text">
              <h3>Public Users</h3>
              <p>Searching content in Aviary is free of charge! Any content made public in Aviary
                is fully searchable in the platform. As a public user, you can search organizations,
                collections, resources, and even transcripts and indexes, as well as navigate content
                using the different visualization tools.</p>
              <p>Ready to start searching?</p>
              <a href="<%= search_catalog_url(q: '', search_field: 'all_fields', utf8: 'âœ“') %>" class="btn btn-primary">Search
                Now!</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="text">
              <h3>Registered Users</h3>
              <p>As a registered user, you can enjoy all the search features offered to
                public users. Additionally you have the ability to request access to private
                content directly from the content administrators. In future releases, registered
                users will be able to annotate content at any level (collection, resource, media, and
                transcript/index).</p>
              <% unless user_signed_in? %>
                <p>Ready to register?</p>
                <a href="javascript://" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#signupmodal" class="btn btn-primary">Join
                  Now!</a>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="img-holder two">
              <%= image_tag("https://#{ENV['S3_HOST_CDN']}/public/reg-user.png") %>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="img-holder three">
              <%= image_tag("https://#{ENV['S3_HOST_CDN']}/public/org-about.png") %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="text">
              <h3>Organizations</h3>
              <p>Take full advantage of enhanced discoverability for your audiovisual collections!
                Putting your content in Aviary is easy thanks to our integrations with Youtube, Vimeo,
                Avalon, SoundCloud, and bulk import functionalities. We offer different plans to fit
                your needs.</p>

              <p>Ready to put your content in Aviary?</p>
              <a href="<%= pricing_path %>" class="btn btn-primary">See Available Plans!</a>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="plans-bottom">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="jumbotron">
            <h1>More about Aviary?</h1>
            <p>Check Aviary's features to learn how our platform can help your organization provide enhanced access to
              your audiovisual collections.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-info btn-lg" href="<%= features_path %>" role="button">View Features</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="jumbotron">
            <h1>Questions?</h1>
            <p>Still have questions about pricing? Get in touch!</p>
            <a class="btn btn-info btn-lg" href="<%= contact_us_path %>" role="button">Contact Us</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>